The following is the discography of Dutch music producer and DJ Afrojack .
His song " Take Over Control " , which features Dutch singer Eva Simons , charted in 10 different countries .
He released his debut EP Lost & Found on December 22 , 2010 .
In 2011 , he was featured on Pitbull 's number 1 hit single " Give Me Everything " along with Ne - Yo and Nayer .
He also contributed to the single " Run the World ( Girls ) " by Beyoncé , who initially did not include his credits on the track but was eventually forced to do so after Afrojack filed a case against her .
His debut album , Forget the World , was released on 16 May 2014 .
